Rescue Dawn;;75;;90;;PG-13;;During the Vietnam War, Dieter Dengler (Christian Bale), a U.S. fighter pilot, is shot down over Laos and taken captive by enemy soldiers. Interned in a POW camp, Dengler and his fellow prisoners (Steve Zahn, Jeremy Davies) endure torture, hunger and illness while they await their chance to escape.;;Drama,War,History;;Werner Herzog;;2007;;Christian Bale,Steve Zahn,Jeremy Davies,Galen Yuen,Apichart Chusakul,Chaiyan "Lek" Chunsuttiwat,Teerawat "Ka-Ge" Mulvilai,Yuttana Muenwaja,Kriangsak Ming-Olo,Pat Healy,Toby Huss;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rescue_dawn